                            <comment id="92745" author="adilger" created="Thu, 28 Aug 2014 20:24:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would probably be better to remove this message from the console entirely.  While it has some marginal usefulness to developers, it isn&apos;t really useful for users and actually caused lustre to fail during testing because of a flood of debug messages to the console (which disables interrupts on the system and can cause serious performance problems).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
